            en: "Chen Zi\u2019ang (661\u2013702), Tang dynasty writer. Du Fu (712\u2013770), Tang dynasty poet. Wang Anshi (1021\u20131086), Northern Song statesman, writer, and thinker. Lu You (1125\u20131210), Southern Song poet. Gong Zizhen (1792\u20131841), Qing dynasty thinker and writer."
